  "text": "\u2022 C prior to freeze drying. Once freeze dried the samples were finely ground with a pestle and mortar. The ground digesta samples were analyzed for titanium dioxide content by the method of [CITATION_1] . Digesta was also analyzed for Ca and P content using ICP-OES after aqua regia digestion. Apparent ileal Ca and P digestibility coefficients were obtained using the following equation:",
